name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 11/ Oka-san says that we are almost ready to use our power once again. The idea is strange because I have never felt powerful. But I trust Oka-san. I understand her power.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 10/ How could weak humans capture the Yokai, the ones who hatched first, the ones with calamitous power?

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 9/ Then the humans appeared. Oka-san says humans are weak. They are weak because they die, and so they live in constant fear of a thing they do not understand. I have never met a human, but they donâ€™t sound weak to me.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 8/ The world was chaos and disorder. Then the Yokai opened their eyes, and their beauty calmed the waters. The rivers returned to their beds. The mountains, feeling shame, found their dignity and drew up to their full height. The world was quiet.â€

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 7/ â€œIn the beginning there were four species, and the Yokais hatched first. The land and the water shook with their calamitous power. Mountains broke apart like brittle leaves. Flowing rivers separated like strands of windblown hair and washed over the green fields.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 6/ Oka-san says that Yokai is an old and special word. It is a special word because it contains two powerful energies: attraction and repulsion. Beauty and disaster.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 5/ What if we decided to walk on our own? What if we decided to dance? What if we decided to leave? Too ugly. I wish I understood ugliness.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 4/ Sometimes I am scared of being left behind. Oka-san says that one day she will make me feet but that feet are strange and often ugly, too ugly for the Yokai, the ones who hatched first. Too ugly, too ugly, she says.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 3/ Or a colorful toy. Or an old song. There are many parts of me in here that are very, very lost. I wonder, too: if we are her children, does that mean I have brothers and sisters? Do they know about me? Are they looking for me? Have they hatched?

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 2/ She says we are her lovely children. When she speaks to me her hair floats across my eyes and her breath collects all around me. It feels like I am floating in her voice. Often, as I drift, I wonder if it is true â€“ if we are children. I feel more like a piece of clothing.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: 1/ "In the beginning, there were four species, and the Yokais hatched first..."  This is the story I have been buried with. Oka-san whispers the words. â€œIn the beginning...the Yokais hatched first...â€ This is her memory, and also her prophecy.

tweet: Voting for our first official derivative art competition is now live in the Discord!  https://t.co/m7B6JL22R8  The team narrowed it down to the Top 10. Who's got your vote?

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Why doesnâ€™t this project have more steam?   A: People will come and go. Hard to find the gems, but this is a long term play here. Market is not rewarding A-List art. We have high quality ideas coming -- don't think any other project has anything of this type.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Could you guys explain a bit more about the future value of the Zodiac Capsules? Will there be any special benefits of holding an entire set of the 12 Zodiac Capsules?  A: Good times are coming for sure.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Does the team like the idea of tokens?   A: We have played around with it but ultimately we want to find other ways to reward holders without the use of tokens for a variety of reasons.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Can you tell us more about the @LivesOfAsuna collaboration?  A: @ZumiDraws is a good friend. We lended some Capsule House IP in exchange for WL spots if that interests you. We're going to be thoughtful but diligent in offering future WL opps.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: When is Capsule House going to be an animated TV series or feature film?  A: We're building a world where our IP is used for interesting things - this all comes back to the IP. Multiyear vision.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Should I leave a capsule on a nifty gateway?  A: No you should not leave a capsule on nifty. It will not qualify towards the 30+ days holderâ€™s raffle due the nature of niftyâ€™s â€˜walletâ€™.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Layer 2 Thoughts/Strategy?  A: Has to fill in an actual technical point for us. If there's anything cool we can pull from Layer2, please let us know.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Seerlight, how accurate is the transition usually between creation in the mind and transference to artwork?  A: Before I start I have a clear picture, but some are lost in translation. As the process goes on, I add on to it so that they come out the same or even better.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Any efforts on building community engagement with each other vs. with the Capsule House team?   A: Capsule Council will be the first branch of this. Want conversations to be more than just speculation of how to improve the community.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Will the 3D models be chibi avatars, rigged and animated? Or is it more bringing of Seerlights worlds to life in 3D?  A: More the former, something usable in games or whatever the next big thing is. The 3D model is of the capsule character. PFP will have a more mature look.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Do you guys have any plans with integrating capsules into www3?  A: Will reach out. A lot of stuff is going into 3D and we are in the process of working on 3D assets, so you can be represented later on in the future. All about future proofing.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Can you guys explain more about the Seerlight Art Installations on the Roadmap?  A: Holders will be given the opportunity to see how amazing their art is. They are the best kept secret of blue chip art right now. More opportunities to expand on this as covid gets better.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Seer had mentioned possibly rewarding minters who never sold. Still something that could happen?  A: Could definitely happen. :)

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Any plans in the future #CapsuleVerse for mythic capsules?  A: Yes! There will be a couple additional features to reward those holding a capsule with a mythic trait.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: What is the possibility of staking Capsules and a token with no financial value?  A: Not an efficient way of distribution, no need to make you guys stake to claim.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: oksami, how many other projects are you working on at once?  A: Acting dev for a few other projects, working on sales infrastructure and contract development. Capsule House is my number 1 priority.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Seerlight, how many other projects are you working on at once?  A: Small art projects and collars, but Capsule House is my baby.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Anything we feel we will be innovators in?  A: Yes - morphing between Capsule to Avatar. Nothing close to the level of quality and scale we are going to embark on. More than enough talent to execute this. Not going to be another 10K PFP drop.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Is this a â€œburnâ€ for a PFP? Otherwise does this not just dilute the market?   A: Finalizing mechanisms but we're not planning on burning the PFP. Instead, morph your capsules around by changing how they are displayed. Scheme where you can keep both. Not going to be diluted.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: When can we expect the PFPs to hatch in 2022?  A: Targeting for the first batch in mid to late January. Batch rollout pace is TBD.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: What is it in particular that inspired/continues to inspire the art style that Seerlight creates?   A: Mostly Ghibli movies. Especially "Spirited Away."

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Seerlight, What do you do to get into your â€œcreative zoneâ€?   A: I usually start after midnight and after I finish everything else I needed to do for the day. I turn on music or play games before I start working, which is every day.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Seerlight, Where do you get the most inspiration for your art?   A: I'm inspired by Asian architecture -- Chinese and Japanese temples. I really look up to Yuumei.

name: CAPSULE HOUSE âœ¨ğŸ’Šâœ¨
tweet: Q: Seerlight, what was your journey like?   A: I started 8 years ago on deviant art, but just about 3 years ago I started to post on IG and grew a following there. Started with painting style and transitioned to line art, which is how I came upon his current style now.
